how to keep your instances running when host is maintained?
By unabling live migration 
a. your VM is migrated to another host in same zone.
b. no properties of vm is changed.
c. It is supported for local SSD vm also but not supported for premetible instances and GPU.
Availablity policy:
a. On Host maintaince: 1.Migrate (by default) 2. Terminate
b. Automatic Restart : Restart a Vm instances when it stoped by non-user instiated reason.
